By":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰D的確我們國家已經同相關國家簽訂條約，確認邊界。<br />\n<br />\n但台灣我們沒有批准他獨立</blockquote><br />\n咁真係咁好意思喇<br />\n<br />\n乜嘢東西南北京條約都簽囇，香港是英國擁有的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c333d4a35c6923db17e6a820d4a923711615e13","tid":456520,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嗰D的確我們國家已經同相關國家簽訂條約，確認邊界。<br />\n<br />\n但台灣我們沒有批准他獨立</blockquote><br />\n咁真係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>好意思喇<br />\n<br />\n乜嘢東西南北京條約都簽囇，香港是英國擁有的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"be57ea21cf59447dd15bbdc19feb3f63eb5812b8","tid":456520,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:54:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嗰D的確我們國家已經同相關國家簽訂條約，確認邊界。<br />\n<br />\n但台灣我們沒有批准他獨立</blockquote><br />\n咁真係咁好意思喇<br />\n<br />\n乜嘢東西南北京條約都簽囇，香港是英國擁有的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n與俄羅斯的邊界問題，其實係90年代我們政府，以平等的地位與俄羅斯正式簽訂，確認邊界。<br />\n<br />\n當年英國首相亦來北京，與鄧小平先生商討相關問題。但我們就不沒有批准香港繼續留英，所以英國首相亦決定歸還香港俾我哋。"},{"pid":"302c47edac806a5772764604f04601f6edf953de","tid":456520,"uid":81156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>嗰D的確我們國家已經同相關國家簽訂條約，確認邊界。<br />\n<br />\n但台灣我們沒有批准他獨立</blockquote><br />\n咁真係咁好意思喇<br />\n<br />\n乜嘢東西南北京條約都簽囇，香港是英國擁有的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n與俄羅斯的邊界問題，其實係90年代我們政府，以平等的地位與俄羅斯正式簽訂，確認邊界。<br />\n<br />\n當年英國首相亦來北京，與鄧小平先生商討相關問題。但我們就不沒有<span style=\"color: red;\">批准</span>香港繼續留英，所以英國首相亦決定歸還香港俾我哋。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你當鄧小平係太上皇阿！批准！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358ca05d5ac134c0c499312907f0837ba8e92b8f","tid":456520,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"我對歷史唔熟<br />\n想知個記者提既地方 依家比邊個佔領左？"},{"pid":"5c68b577bbff5d1148b477656ab0b863be1fc33c","tid":456520,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>嗰D的確我們國家已經同相關國家簽訂條約，確認邊界。<br />\n<br />\n但台灣我們沒有批准他獨立</blockquote><br />\n咁真係咁好意思喇<br />\n<br />\n乜嘢東西南北京條約都簽囇，香港是英國擁有的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n與俄羅斯的邊界問題，其實係90年代我們政府，以平等的地位與俄羅斯正式簽訂，確認邊界。<br />\n<br />\n當年英國首相亦來北京，與鄧小平先生商討相關問題。但我們就不沒有<span style=\"color: red;\">批准</span>香港繼續留英，所以英國首相亦決定歸還香港俾我哋。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你當鄧小平係太上皇阿！批准！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪撚理啲五毛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec30e42dabc2fc697ce1aa6b6422afc32c3d7c2","tid":456520,"uid":81156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n咪撚理啲五毛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsor望到呢句真係o咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7726ea9431a26078536c88f5bb23551463d2d311","tid":456520,"uid":50408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:25:56.000Z","msg":"前兩個回覆先講完台灣，之後個回覆就話唔使成日拉台灣嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢可以侵略人，人都可以侵略佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁嘈乜尖閣諸島<img src=\"/assets/faces/n