地位與俄羅斯正式簽訂，確認邊界。<br />\n<br />\n當年英國首相亦來北京，與鄧小平先生商討相關問題。但我們就不沒有<span style=\"color: red;\">批准</span>香港繼續留英，所以英國首相亦決定歸還香港俾我哋。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你當鄧小平係太上皇阿！批准！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔需要，英國基本上等1997然後拒絕歸還香港就可以。但佢哋就知道自己唔可能再好似當年咁蝦我哋國家。所以咪要死死氣去北京求鄧小平唔好收香港。但我哋冇同意佢哋的請求，先有中英聯合聲明，歸還香港姐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4499890fb1d28177581a9983c6db234d48046b5","tid":456520,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰D的確我們國家已經同相關國家簽訂條約，確認邊界。<br />\n<br />\n但台灣我們沒有批准他獨立</blockquote><br />\n喂喂<br />\n咁點解唔宣布喺台灣實行國歌法？"},{"pid":"2009a6f08e3435e5fbd6db1545548f5db0ce09eb","tid":456520,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>海參崴</blockquote><br />\n俄佬一於起個名叫征服東方 VLADIVOSTOK<br />\n<br />\n外交部聽到死狗咁款</blockquote><br />\n我們可以征服人<br />\n人哋自然可以征服我哋<br />\n<br />\n台灣有本事都可以即刻宣佈獨立，如果美國爸爸批准的話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔洗成日將台灣拉埋一齊講。台灣有俄羅斯咁的實力咩？點可能相提並論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開始了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f64c395ad10d6f1ba11b06c2724e0e3924a5a2","tid":456520,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E8%8F%AF%E6%98%A5%E7%91%A9%E7%84%A1%E9%81%BF%E7%AD%94%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-